comment.narrative:
1) Support with SDG awareness raising campaign;
2) Support civil society engagement in SDGs implementation and monitoring;
3) Mainstream SDG targets and indicators into national plans through support of MNE and 5 working groups;
4) Work with Academia to increase awareness of SDGs using innovative mechanisms (Hackathon, digitalization of SDG Game);
5) Enhance capacity of Committee on Statistics through trainings/seminars;
6) Finalize implementation of DFA and RIA in Kazakhstan

1) Created 17 videos on SDGs with participation of a range of experts. The videos will be used as a tool of SDG awareness raising among population and as a pre-requisite to the Digital Mission 2030 Game;
2) Supported Committee on Statistics with organizing a series of workshops to finalize a nationalized set of SDG indicators;
3) Targets and indicators will be mainstreamed in national plans by the result of the SDG Coordination council meeting to be held in 2021.
4) Organized a 3 day virtual Hackathon to digitalize Mission 2030 game. The game is developed by a young tech specialist, who won the Hackathon. 
5) Enhanced capacity of Com Stat in providing trainings on methodologies to calculate SDG indicators with a focus on environmental and gender-related indicators.
6) The DFA is finalized with involvement of the national think tank JSC Economic Research Institute . The report will be validated by the Government of RK.

1) Strengthen the national coordination mechanism for the SDGs implementation, monitoring and reporting: address the most pressing capacity of ERI in VNR preparation, provide technical support to preapre a quality VNR in compliance with the reporting guidelines prepared by the UNDG.
2) Facilitate participation of the MNE in the second global workshop for the 2019 VNR countries to be held in Bonn, on 19-20 February 2019;
3) Organize a first forum on the SDGs on the auspices of the Astana Economic Forum
4) Provide technical assistance for the SDGs nationalization and localization process in Kazakhstan;
5) Support national statistical capacity
6) Establish a dialogue on SDG financing
